OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FA couple who threw their elderly dog
OL,7,Finto a canal have been handed a ten
OL,8,Fyear animal ban.
OL,10,FTerrence Boyd, 34, and his 32-year-old
OL,11,Fwife Sadie Boyd were captured on CCTV
OL,12,Fon 27 August 2025 carrying their
OL,13,Fterrier Maddie in a black bin bag.
OL,15,FThe couple took the dog to the Leeds
OL,16,Fand Liverpool canal close to their
OL,17,Fhome in Brierfield, where they threw
OL,18,Fher into the water.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
