FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FA dog walker saw them throw Maddie
OL,7,Finto the canal, but when questioned
OL,8,Fthe couple said it only contained
OL,9,Fclothes.
OL,11,FBut when Maddie's head appeared from
OL,12,Fthe bag, a member of the public jumped
OL,13,Finto the water and tried to save her.
OL,15,FLancashire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,16,Fwere also called to help rescue the
OL,17,Fdog. After she was saved, they took
OL,18,Fher to the local vets.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FAlthough she survived, Maddie's
OL,7,Fcondition worsened in the days that
OL,8,Ffollowed and she was put to sleep to
OL,9,Fprevent further suffering.
OL,11,FIt was discovered that Maddie was
OL,12,Fmicrochipped to Sadie Boyle's address
OL,13,Fand the couple were arrested at their
OL,14,Fhome later that day on suspicion of
OL,15,Fanimal welfare offences.
OL,17,FPolice also removed seven underweight
OL,18,Fkittens from the property because of
OL,19,Fwelfare concerns.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
