FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FA corn snake who was cold and living
OL,7,Fin an enclosure with no heating or
OL,8,Fsuitable light was passed into the
OL,9,Fcare of an exotic specialist. The
OL,10,Fsurviving kittens were rehomed by the
OL,11,FRSPCA.
OL,13,FMagistrates were told the house was
OL,14,Funsanitary with large piles of pet
OL,15,Ffaeces seen upstairs and mice running
OL,16,Faround the kitchen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
