PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FIn her written evidence to the court
OL,7,Fthe vet who treated Maddie, said: "On
OL,8,Fclinical examination, Maddie was
OL,9,Fhypothermic, with a temperature of
OL,10,F33.2C. She was severely malnourished,
OL,11,Fwith significant muscle atrophy."
OL,13,FTerrence, who pleaded guilty to two
OL,14,FAnimal Welfare Act offences in
OL,15,Frelation to Maddie, plus seven kittens
OL,16,Fand a corn snake, were prosecuted by
OL,17,Fthe RSPCA after the charity was called
OL,18,Fin to investigate.
OL,26,@oD@cOUrD@EOXsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
