FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FAt Burnley Magistrates Court on
OL,7,FWednesday 24 June Maddie's owners, the
OL,8,Fcouple were both sentenced to eight
OL,9,Fweeks custody, suspended for 12
OL,10,Fmonths, and disqualified from keeping
OL,11,Fanimals for ten years.
OL,13,FAll seven kittens found at the address
OL,14,Fwere malnourished and urine-soaked.
OL,15,FFour of them were hypothermic and
OL,16,Fneeded warming up.
OL,18,FThe smallest female, weighing only 735
OL,19,Fgrams (26oz), was recumbent and about
OL,20,Fto have a seizure and was put to sleep
OL,21,Fby the vet on welfare grounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,FThe couple were both ordered to
OL,7,Fcomplete 20 Rehabilitation Activity
OL,8,FRequirement Days and pay a victim
OL,9,Fsurcharge of #154 each.
OL,11,FSpeaking after sentencing RSPCA Chief
OL,12,FInspector Nix said: "What happened to
OL,13,FMaddie was horrifying and this
OL,14,Fincident was understandably the cause
OL,15,Fof great distress to people who were
OL,16,Fat the scene, the emergency services
OL,17,Fand the wider local community.
OL,26,@tD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782915513
OL,3,CCouple handed ten year animal ban for
OL,4,Cthrowing elderly dog into canal
OL,6,F"It was heartbreaking that Maddie's
OL,7,Fcondition deteriorated and she
OL,8,Fultimately could not be saved. I hope
OL,9,Fpeople will take some small comfort in
OL,10,Fthe fact that those responsible for
OL,11,Fthis shocking incident were able to be
OL,12,Fheld to account for their actions and
OL,13,Fwill not be able to keep animals for
OL,14,Fthe foreseeable future."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
